{"tid":759882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5女生租用快艇　撞環保船8傷","createTime":"2018-07-29T05:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T05:17:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7a11b2bf8c939aa408a027f171daffe073416b38","tid":759882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180729/20463303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463303&d=%2BE7Kq8wY7GpSYtDHNsGSHE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=cd28d768\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463303&h=91a8b071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180729/20463303</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月29日 <br />\n<br />\n5女生租用快艇　撞環保船8傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180729/large/a0406a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180729%2Flarge%2Fa0406a.gif&h=3817d4d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■快艇沉沒後僅剩船頭露出海面，附近船家趕至救人。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】南丫島昨發生撞船意外，5名大學女生租用一艘快艇出海，途中與另一艘環保船相撞後沉沒，環保船的船長及一名船員亦告受傷。幸當時有船隻經過，將快艇的5名女生及船家救起。事件中共8人受傷，其中4人送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由駛經船家救起<br />\n<br />\n8名傷者包括3男5女（介乎19至50歲），全部輕傷，送院時清醒。事發昨午1時許，5名大學女生租用一艘快艇出海，當快艇駛至榕樹灣碼頭對開約300米海面時，與一艘在海面執垃圾的環保船相撞，其中快艇翻船沉沒。此時有其他船家駛經，見狀立即救起5名女生及快艇的船家。而環保船當時有船長及一名船員，兩人亦受傷，其中船員撞傷頭部。<br />\n<br />\n消防接報趕往救援，水警輪在榕樹灣碼頭戒備，其後8名傷者在碼頭上岸，送往榕樹灣診所作初步治理。其中環保船船長及船員兩人，與另外兩名女傷者，分別轉送港島醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據環保船船長梁先生稱，事發時聽到「砰」一聲巨響，即發生撞船意外，所見對方的快艇超過20呎長。梁與其船員可自行落救護車，其中船員額頭敷有紗布。而快艇上其中一名女傷者送院時，可見她手踭擦損。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫文學  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n西貢遊船河暢泳　雙程漢溺斃<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n尖沙嘴港鐵站　內地童就地大便"},{"pid":"0f288cb5f98d1cb60dcd51ff11203ee5f04afedb","tid":759882,"uid":14073,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:05:51.000Z","msg":"女人揸船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0f7d1583ce7b509a34caf879945ef6a84e73b7","tid":759882,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35e33cc917cd68bfce91cb44148830b4b90da710","tid":759882,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:09:26.000Z","msg":"15米以下的機動遊樂船, 係要牌"},{"pid":"c4a38f8df6106355238b4c259199901dacc24dd5","tid":759882,"uid":78399,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc0f7d1583ce7b509a34caf879945ef6a84e73b7","tid":759882,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:09:30.000Z","msg":"當快艇駛至榕樹灣碼頭對開約300米海面時，與一艘在海面執垃圾的環保船相撞，其中快艇翻船沉沒。此時有其他船家駛經，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">見狀立即救起5名女生及快艇的船家。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n睇下內文先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe9c14d7875f9c83b7631c242b3c27dc55854c0","tid":759882,"uid":124941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4a38f8df6106355238b4c259199901dacc24dd5","tid":759882,"uid":78399,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc0f7d1583ce7b509a34caf879945ef6a84e73b7","tid":759882,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:09:30.000Z","msg":"當快艇駛至榕樹灣碼頭對開約300米海面時，與一艘在海面執垃圾的環保船相撞，其中快艇翻船沉沒。此時有其他船家駛經，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">見狀立即救起5名女生及快艇的船家。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n睇下內文先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm